column2: SELECT u.up_CID as CID,   p.objID, p.ra, p.dec,   dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,  p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_r, p.extinction_u, p.extinction_r,  pz.z, pz.zErr FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN PhotoObj p ON p.objID = x.objID  JOIN Photoz pz ON pz.ObjID = x.objID ORDER by x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
